        "created_at": "2021-03-30T19:02:12.808Z",
        "cooked": "<p>One canâ€™t zoom into a picture when drawing on it. This is necessary to be able to draw precise lines though (e.g. when you want to highlight some small detail).</p>\n<p><strong>Standard gestures</strong> are<br>\n1 Finger - <em>draw</em><br>\n2 Fingers - <em>zoom and move in the picture</em></p>\n<p><strong>Implementations</strong><br>\nIf you want to get an example of what I mean open up Telegram or WhatsApp, open a chat, select a picture, click on the pen and try zooming. It just feels natural to be able to do this.<br>\nSo please implement it.</p>",
