        "created_at": "2025-05-27T10:29:25.811Z",
        "cooked": "<p>This should be added to the blur feature, not just the drawing feature. Image zooming is very needed for blurring smaller or distant faces that the automatic face blur feature does not detect. This is extremely tedious without the ability to scroll in. Alternatively, the face-blur feature can be improved for smaller or more distant faces to prevent this from being an issue in the first place.</p>",
